InfluenceZ

This project is an influencer platform where brands can manage influencer campaigns and influencers can apply for them. The platform has two main roles: Brand and Influencer.
Features

    Brands can create campaigns, view influencers, and accept/reject applicants.

    Influencers can apply to campaigns based on their profile and stats.

    Real-time updates on campaign status and influencer interactions.

Live Demo

You can access the live demo here:
https://influen-z-git-main-dasun-illangasinghes-projects.vercel.app/

